thread.title: Russia to expel 23 UK diplomats over Skripal spat

title: Russia to expel 23 UK diplomats over Skripal spat
text:
Russia to expel 23 UK diplomats over Skripal spat Saturday, March 17, 2018 - 01:57 
Russia has said 23 British diplomats must leave within a week amid the fallout from the use of a nerve agent targeting Sergei skripal and his daughter on UK soil. The move comes after the UK decided to kick out 23 Russians earlier in the week.
